00:50:13,805 --> 00:50:40,788
If my street is in the yellow category, when will you be able to allocate funding towards medium grade road problems? It doesn't go so far as to answer that question, because that's not a question for the DPW to answer, but for a budget directorship to answer. But it at least goes farther than most other identified, at least colloquially, needs in the city go.

114
00:50:43,319 --> 00:51:11,686
And I think that at least starts to demonstrate some of what we need because there's so much else to talk about. When I was thinking about need identification prior to this meeting, I'm struck by sort of we have different buckets or different categories of semi-identified needs. We have a capital improvement plan, though it's

